%e9%99%84%e6%b0%91%2c425%2c20220624%2c3/pdf"},"JID":"TYDM,110,附民,425,20220624,3","JYEAR":"110","JCASE":"附民","JNO":"425","JDATE":"20220624","JTITLE":"請求賠償損害"}